      StompSession.Subscription DefaultStompSession.subscribe(StompHeaders headers, StompFrameHandler handler) 
      StompSession.Subscription StompSession.subscribe(StompHeaders headers, StompFrameHandler handler)
      An overloaded version of StompSession.subscribe(String, StompFrameHandler) with full StompHeaders instead of just a destination.
      StompSession.Subscription DefaultStompSession.subscribe(java.lang.String destination, StompFrameHandler handler) 
      StompSession.Subscription StompSession.subscribe(java.lang.String destination, StompFrameHandler handler)
      Subscribe to the given destination by sending a SUBSCRIBE frame and handle received messages with the specified StompFrameHandler.
